productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
My co-worker Rey has one of these. He says it looks uneven.
My neighbor Georgie has one of these. She works as a busboy and she says it looks brown.
My co-worker Alek has one of these. He says it looks white.
This Bedfordshire works quite well. It pointedly improves my golf by a lot.
